//! # Design by Contract
//!
//! Comprehensive contract system for program verification:
//!
//! - **Static Verification**: Compile-time proof via SMT solving
//! - **Runtime Checking**: Configurable assertion checking at runtime
//! - **Contract Inheritance**: Liskov Substitution Principle enforcement
//! - **Documentation**: Contracts serve as executable specifications
//!
//! ## Contract Annotations
//!
//! ```quanta
//! @requires(n >= 0)
//! @ensures(result >= 0)
//! @ensures(result * result <= n)
//! @ensures((result + 1) * (result + 1) > n)
//! fn isqrt(n: i64) -> i64 {
//!     // Implementation
//! }
//! ```
//!
//! ## Type Invariants
//!
//! ```quanta
//! @invariant(self.len >= 0)
//! @invariant(self.capacity >= self.len)
//! struct Vec<T> {
//!     data: *mut T,
//!     len: usize,
//!     capacity: usize,
//! }
//! ```
//!
//! ## Loop Contracts
//!
//! ```quanta
//! @invariant(0 <= i && i <= n)
//! @invariant(sum == i * (i - 1) / 2)
//! @decreases(n - i)
//! while i < n {
//!     sum += i;
//!     i += 1;
//! }
//! ```

module quantalang::contracts

